Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.78,0:00:15.54,Opening,,0,0,0,,My right hand holds a bowl of gold,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.54,0:00:19.79,Opening,,0,0,0,,And my left holds one of silver.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.79,0:00:24.46,Opening,,0,0,0,,Never one without the other,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.46,0:00:37.70,Opening,,0,0,0,,Two unseen bowls for each of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.70,0:00:45.98,Opening,,0,0,0,,The golden one is filled with joy,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.98,0:00:53.45,Opening,,0,0,0,,shining warmly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.45,0:00:57.99,Opening,,0,0,0,,Since we met, my golden bowl
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.99,0:01:05.26,Opening,,0,0,0,,cannot hold all my happiness and love.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.83,0:01:15.40,Opening,,0,0,0,,Golden joy, silver sadness,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.40,0:01:22.75,Opening,,0,0,0,,I would leave my past behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.75,0:01:27.48,Opening,,0,0,0,,For you, for the sake of love,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.48,0:01:34.42,Opening,,0,0,0,,I would empty the bowls of my past.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.82,0:02:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Miya-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.65,0:02:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Miya-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.82,0:02:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Miya-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.78,0:02:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry Nanako-san. I'm truly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.52,0:02:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted you to swim with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.79,0:02:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Nanako-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.46,0:02:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.86,0:02:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.64,0:02:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{ b1}23. The Forbidden Gift{ b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.76,0:03:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,My Dear Brother... this is my first real truancy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.37,0:03:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,After what happened, I couldn't face school today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.57,0:03:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I still feel overwhelmed by all that happened there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.89,0:03:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to avoid dealing with reality a while longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.92,0:03:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you? How's your fever?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.53,0:03:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a bit tired, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.90,0:03:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll feel better this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.04,0:03:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Try some hot lemonade.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.46,0:03:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you, Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.13,0:03:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I can call a taxi to take you to the hospital...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.42,0:04:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok. If my fever goes over 36.7.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.28,0:04:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.59,0:04:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,A cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.78,0:04:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, she has a low fever and feels weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.41,0:04:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,She called as I was leaving, so I couldn't really talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.33,0:04:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.24,0:04:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I can give her a message, if you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.37,0:04:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm stopping at her house on my way home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.78,0:04:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.87,0:05:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I had no fever, yet somehow I wasn't myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.47,0:05:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Somehow I was weary to my very bones,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.21,0:05:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,...and I continued to have terrifying nightmares.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.91,0:05:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoko stopped by on her way home from school.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.22,0:05:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you mind if we went to the beach?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.02,0:05:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.37,0:05:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Playing sick, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.97,0:05:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What a phony you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.91,0:05:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You owe me for the cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.34,0:05:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.78,0:05:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Be nice, or I'll charge you interest!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.85,0:05:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, here's the first payment then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.72,0:05:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Here! A souvenir, from the lake!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.54,0:05:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, great!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.93,0:06:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess what! Miya-sama was looking for you today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.97,0:06:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.83,0:06:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what was it that happened at her place?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.83,0:06:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No... nothing to speak of! I had such a great time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.40,0:06:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What a luxurious mansion!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.24,0:06:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Walking around, enjoying the view, listening to music...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.08,0:06:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So! How about a race? Let's race!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.12,0:06:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,To the breakwater up ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.04,0:06:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.36,0:06:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.49,0:06:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,All right then! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.24,0:06:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.78,0:06:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Phone call for you... From Ichinomiya-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.22,0:06:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.18,0:06:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.88,0:06:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take it in my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.13,0:07:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.41,0:07:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard you were absent today...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.90,0:07:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have a cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.37,0:07:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.20,0:07:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.02,0:07:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I... well... my fever is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.33,0:07:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So... I'll see your smiling face again at school tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.48,0:07:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... Yes! I'll be at school tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.13,0:07:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.35,0:07:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, staying home had nothing to do with what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.89,0:07:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No... nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.96,0:07:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.09,0:07:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It was just because you looked so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.50,0:07:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Playing a little trick on you was irresistible... that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.84,0:07:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.74,0:07:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Changing the subject... it was decided at today's Sorority meeting,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.68,0:08:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,...that junior members will serve the guests at my birthday party.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.56,0:08:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't you help us, Nanako-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.26,0:08:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,My Dear Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.66,0:08:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Miya-sama's voice made my whole body become tense.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.14,0:08:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,My hand on the receiver was wet with cold sweat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.10,0:08:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't wait for the conversation to end.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.06,0:08:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.47,0:08:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.48,0:08:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But... those things that happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.34,0:08:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't talk about them. To anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.16,0:08:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Nanako-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.23,0:08:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,...did you decide on a present for Miya-sama's birthday?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.13,0:08:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, not yet. What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.96,0:08:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a secret!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.43,0:08:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You've seen them, the other members...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.12,0:09:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,...they're all trying to find out what each other's presents are.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.05,0:09:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,They want to buy Miya-sama's favor with expensive gifts.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.75,0:09:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.45,0:09:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I can tell you, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.45,0:09:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell the other members.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.94,0:09:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Red roses?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.36,0:09:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, the gorgeous red roses that she loves...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.79,0:09:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to fill up her banquet room with them!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.73,0:09:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I arranged it all with the flower shop at the Hotel Royale.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.00,0:09:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.94,0:09:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, sorry! I was held up at my club.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.14,0:09:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, gorgeous!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.84,0:09:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,...2,3,4,5,6 zeros!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.06,0:09:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Those things are all two or three zeros off!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.18,0:09:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you lost your mind, Nanako?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.73,0:09:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Just looking!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.21,0:09:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't afford it, even if I stand on my head!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.94,0:09:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That would be my Dad's monthly salary!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.91,0:09:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.37,0:10:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.48,0:10:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.37,0:10:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Medusa-no-Kimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.91,0:10:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That will be all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.25,0:10:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Certainly. It's a pleasure to serve you, madam.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.34,0:10:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Please give our regards to your father and mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.93,0:10:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! She must have bought a present for Miya-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.26,0:10:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.93,0:10:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,All the nice things are too expensive for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.01,0:10:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing I can afford here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.23,0:10:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Give up on the idea of competing with money.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.40,0:10:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.60,0:10:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have any, in the first place...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.94,0:10:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks a lot! I'll tell Father that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.82,0:10:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead you can compete with... this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.21,0:10:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,This, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.05,0:10:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes indeed! How about your famous cookies?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.08,0:10:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just the same old thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.04,0:10:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Having your own style is really {\i1}it{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.00,0:10:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It is so much like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.03,0:10:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We all call you "Cookie Nanako"!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.63,0:11:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.49,0:11:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,To my Dad, Mom, brother, and even our hamster, Pochi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.20,0:11:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Pochi too?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.17,0:11:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.45,0:11:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.81,0:11:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to call you at this early hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.92,0:11:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Quite all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.71,0:11:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it the day you go to the promontory?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.86,0:11:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, to the promontory, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.74,0:11:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,There's still a wisp of fog...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.47,0:11:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, the ocean is beautiful here, this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.77,0:11:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's quiet... calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.52,0:11:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's always like this when I come to visit you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.62,0:11:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You know already...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.89,0:12:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,...that Fukiko-sama will be turning 18, soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.62,0:12:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the anniversary of your mother's death?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.25,0:12:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Time passes by, it's already been 3 years since your Mother died.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.81,0:12:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Then, your recommendation got me into Seiran Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.19,0:12:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You rented an apartment for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.80,0:12:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,...and gave me a monthly allowance to live on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.20,0:12:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.40,0:12:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really nothing to the Ichinomiya family.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.14,0:12:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though we had different mothers,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.54,0:12:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,...we do share the same father.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.95,0:13:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, my birthday party is this coming Sunday.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.62,0:13:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't you come? Please?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.09,0:13:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Being my only sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.74,0:13:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy 18th birthday, Miya-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.72,0:13:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.90,0:13:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.52,0:13:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I love it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.00,0:13:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,A diamond necklace, made in Italy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.39,0:13:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.83,0:13:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.76,0:13:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Your favorite French perfume.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.20,0:13:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.27,0:13:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.87,0:14:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,A rose, your favorite kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.55,0:14:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And, in celebration of your 18th birthday,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.41,0:14:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,...another one thousand, seven hundred, and ninety nine!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.22,0:14:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.29,0:14:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,How incredibly beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.63,0:14:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.10,0:14:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at these presents! Will she really like mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.91,0:14:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako-san, what are you doing? It's your turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.85,0:14:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha... happy Birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.81,0:14:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... Here. Backed for you, from my sincere heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.19,0:14:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Home-made? Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.69,0:14:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.87,0:15:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Does anyone have any more gifts to present?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.24,0:15:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,In 30 minutes, our guests will be arriving.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.81,0:15:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, junior members should prepare to serve our guests, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.93,0:15:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.50,0:15:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Have some! This is port wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.74,0:15:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome! Hors d'oervres are being served over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.56,0:16:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn, I think we're a little late.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.80,0:16:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.33,0:16:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.23,0:16:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome! We'll take care of your things...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.95,0:16:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you sign the guest register, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.01,0:16:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.39,0:17:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,My brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.53,0:17:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... Good evening!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.22,0:17:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi! You look very nice today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.05,0:17:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I had such a wonderful time at the university fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.94,0:17:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.68,0:17:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.02,0:17:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.98,0:17:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.70,0:17:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.49,0:17:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope it's not going to stain.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.06,0:17:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.77,0:17:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.50,0:17:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,There are guests over there who need fresh drinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.59,0:17:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... of course! Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.11,0:17:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I forced him to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.78,0:18:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise he would have spent all day in the lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.19,0:18:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.22,0:18:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to barge in like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.39,0:18:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.33,0:18:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.25,0:18:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Mariko-san! More whisky and water.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.51,0:18:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Making some now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.55,0:18:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.55,0:18:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.42,0:18:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you care for whisky and water?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.38,0:18:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.56,0:18:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.05,0:18:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste-sama! When did you get here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.76,0:18:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been here a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.23,0:18:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You just didn't notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.31,0:18:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.57,0:18:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm kidding. I just got here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.81,0:18:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Saint-Juste-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.07,0:18:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't you play something?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.97,0:18:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't you please?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.15,0:18:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Play something for Miya-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.98,0:18:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.71,0:19:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, for the Guest of Honor then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.60,0:19:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It was unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.60,0:19:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,At such a wonderful party,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.73,0:19:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,...I could never have guessed what would happen next.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.94,0:19:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,No one could have.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.25,0:20:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the song!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.82,0:20:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The one Miya-sama played at her country home!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.10,0:21:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You... you shameless bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.61,0:21:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,"Shameless bitch"?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.84,0:21:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Fukiko-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.90,0:21:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Fukiko-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.30,0:21:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, everyone... please go on with the party...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.66,0:21:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll be back shortly... so please... enjoy yourselves... please!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.23,0:21:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Why, Fukiko-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.14,0:21:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What could I have done?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.44,0:21:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That song!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.81,0:21:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,"That song"?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.41,0:21:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That melody...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.41,0:21:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,...is the one I hate the most in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.74,0:21:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.93,0:21:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I was sure you loved that song!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.37,0:21:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You used to play it! I've heard you play it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.36,0:22:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Many times! Over and over!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.37,0:22:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Fukiko-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.72,0:22:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.24,0:22:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I never wanted you here anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.16,0:22:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu-san... we can take you home in our car.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.53,0:22:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,No thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.41,0:22:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But, it's raining!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.67,0:22:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako-san, watch what you're doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.17,0:22:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let a man talk you into sharing your umbrella!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.75,0:22:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That incident brought an end to the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.82,0:23:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Neither Mariko-san nor I knew what to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.67,0:23:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We walked to the station without a word.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.50,0:23:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Such a happy little party...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.37,0:23:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,...to end in such a violent storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.06,0:24:14.26,Ending,,0,0,0,,I dreamed I was chasing a rainbow...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.26,0:24:19.73,Ending,,0,0,0,,Then the rainbow I was chasing was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.20,0:24:25.34,Ending,,0,0,0,,Before, I had no strength, no will.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.34,0:24:30.81,Ending,,0,0,0,,But now because of you, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.55,0:24:37.09,Ending,,0,0,0,,Feelings of love, like raindrops
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.09,0:24:42.56,Ending,,0,0,0,,Come pouring from the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.56,0:24:45.29,Ending,,0,0,0,,This is surely a game
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.29,0:24:48.10,Ending,,0,0,0,,Of some mischievous fairy...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.10,0:24:50.50,Ending,,0,0,0,,Always dancing,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.50,0:24:55.77,Ending,,0,0,0,,Always capricious...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.48,0:25:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Though Rei played a song she thought Fukiko loved,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.62,0:25:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,...it somehow caused Fukiko to explode at her with rage.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.95,0:25:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Rei seeks out an explanation from Takashi,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.70,0:25:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,...to ease her torment,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.41,0:25:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,...and learns of the shocking events of 6 years earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.90,0:25:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Next episode: Encore
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.28,0:25:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, Dear Brother... There is no end to my tears...
